data.description: Move in ready! This three bedroom, two bath, two year old custom home with a fenced in backyard and a two car garage located in Olde Towne SD is the perfect place to call Home. There is a large double gate on the back fence that opens up to a pond behind the house. The open floor plan is great for entertaining family and friends. Do not miss out on this one!
